{"tid":531283,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"上古世紀公會 <Valkyrie> 招收長期玩家","createTime":"2018-01-16T15:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T23:55:37.000Z","uid":140368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00898c1a532080c37718bed5d7d7546f80f8ff89","tid":531283,"uid":140368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"Valkyrie於2013年上古世紀(美服)創立, 由一班東大陸熱血玩家努力經營. 事隔4年, 本公會轉戰台服, 再續上古情! 現招收有志之士加入本會! <br />\n<br />\n本會每星期設有公會活動, 包括: 跑商 (海/陸), 搶劫西大陸, 打副本, 挑戰世界王 etc.<br />\n<br />\n種族: 哈里蘭/獸人族<br />\n入會條件: 必須有discord (語音程式)  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FeqSEn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FFeqSEn&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyu54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fba0e504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/FeqSEn</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/232247_b2c269995b392fade839ffbb75cc9ffb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F232247_b2c269995b392fade839ffbb75cc9ffb.jpg&h=5628bb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯絡資料: 吳冠仔(會長)<br />\n樂少(副會長)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/232621_c441c3a4958399016e85fc9c65104936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F232621_c441c3a4958399016e85fc9c65104936.jpg&h=ceee4805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/232635_5ba33513fc88866444419f95cd9c6631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F232635_5ba33513fc88866444419f95cd9c6631.jpg&h=843c5f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/232701_6399cbe25bf725372ea28d82fb19d9f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F232701_6399